Package me.jamiemansfield.lorenz.io.parser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MappingsParser
    A parser for a given mappings format, that is built upon Guava's LineProcessor.
    MappingsReader
    Represents a reader that parses mappings from a BufferedReader, using a MappingsParser.
    SrgParser
    The mappings parser for the SRG format.
    SrgReader
    An implementation of MappingsReader for the SRG format.
